Title: Black Water
Plot: A dead body of a 2-year-missing Navy officer appears on the bottom of a lake. The team investigates the case with a help of a private detective. Meanwhile, a famous family offers a lot of money in exchange for the information about the missing body. The team is surprised when a bullet is found in a car. Now the dissapereance becomes a murder...
Writer: Juan Carlos Coto, John C. Kelley
GuestStars: Mike Starr, Michael Weaver, Robin Riker, Brian Dietzen, Mark D. Espinoza, Lorna Scott, Jimmy Palumbo
